lead_paragraph: Jim Boeheim quickly scoffed at what has become an almost-constant suggestion — that it was a rough season for the Syracuse coach who has been associated with the school for more than a half-century.

headline.print_headline: Syracuse's Boeheim Scoffs at Idea That It Was Rough Season
